abstract: NFL Roundup; NFL is investigating domestic dispute involving Cleveland Browns backup quarterback Johnny Manziel, who could face punishment from league; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Cleveland Coach Mike Pettine said Monday that the league was investigating a domestic dispute last week involving Manziel, the team’s backup.

headline.main: Johnny Manziel Faces League Review After Dispute With Girlfriend
headline.print_headline: Manziel Set for Inquiry After Dispute With Woman
